{"tid":1493424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"順著侵侵的思維去諗，如何能成功令支爆發生?","createTime":"2019-08-21T08:41:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T14:30:43.000Z","uid":29510,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"25bfb72407c6525b9f6461b36ae4a0bec37cf183","tid":1493424,"uid":29510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:41:15.000Z","msg":"除左迫大陸出老解外，其實係咪仲存左其他空間去迫使中國大陸經濟衰退？<br />\n明顯侵侵想令中國支爆，但係未成功，因為雖然美國係第一大經濟體，但係只有自己一個國家對付支那，都未必穩操勝劵<br />\n所以我認為，國際支持者可以做以下兩點：<br />\n<br />\n1. 全球支持者發起罷買中國貨<br />\n我見到上星期世界各地（巴黎、倫敦及柏林、悉尼、墨爾本、阿得雷德、布里斯班等等），都有人發起集會支援香港，假如呢個時候我地呼籲其他地方o既支持者罷買中國貨，中國都幾頭痕<br />\n<br />\n支持者人數有限，但呢個唔係要實際o既經濟作用，而<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係一種意識形態上ｏ既威嚇，將中國海外經濟綑綁香港人o既抗爭</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當然罷買中國貨,講就易, 做就難, 但係我唔撚理你實際上有冇偷偷地買, 口頭上都要大大聲講罷買中國貨，對中共做成一種無形壓力，4面受敵o既感覺<br />\n<br />\n2. 繼8964後，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重新將中國妖魔化</span></span><br />\n另一方面，隨住twitter, facebook出左通告話中國利用媒體醜化香港示威,手頭上亦持有證據，封鎖左幾百個3毛Account，即係話外國領頭o既媒體已經企緊香港人呢邊<br />\n<br />\n呢單野爆出左，中國繼8964後花30年努力辛苦經營o既國際形象已經下降, 我地呢個時候,係咪應該要努力發掘中國o既黑材料, 例如提醒國際有8964呢件事、中國人權問題、劉曉波、艾未未、黑心奶粉等等<br />\n務求發起全球不信任支那行動<br />\n<br />\n呢種樣同時係助攻緊侵侵同對應返上年美國呼籲全球唔好用華為5G技術<br />\n上年歐洲都唔撚理侵侵，而家形勢又再唔同左，我地要助攻侵侵、各國領導<br />\n因為各國都同大陸有貿易關係，元首對中國態度上點都會留一線, 唔會出咁多聲<br />\n<br />\n所以,元首唔方便o既野, 就由平民發起<br />\n<br />\n中共而家其實面對住貿易戰、經濟下行、相繼有廠商搬去印度、越南等等地方，頭痕到爆，只係故作鎮定<br />\n<br />\n講打，中共有核彈、解放軍，我地冇可能贏，惟有靠經濟上，睇下有冇可能扭轉"},{"pid":"3adca3d573acddbc34ff3539ea36d757cf4aed15","tid":1493424,"uid":40470,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:52:58.000Z","msg":"強国所有外資企業一次過撤資<br />\n<br />\n用來做交易既人仔換返自己貨幣走佬，必爆！"},{"pid":"f918cb116b25412eef70d7abb066fce3babaef57","tid":1493424,"uid":4811,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:54:48.000Z","msg":"由外而內再到返外⋯⋯"},{"pid":"89941d4d4574e431000daab7ba8b11484a07a6de","tid":1493424,"uid":197492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:56:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"51cd6c1b84bb14a6dde7885a9ba39959bbf95198","tid":1493424,"uid":92188,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:57:48.000Z","msg":"中國已經r爛塊面，之前仲想包裝自己做文明大國，輸出劣性文化"},{"pid":"271c13479620255d8f70b3594f0fa472a26c3877","tid":1493424,"uid":271027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:57:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aacb52f23536a24f9d59a6abc7e529fe1fecff52","tid":1493424,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:58:11.000Z","msg":"必須要令中共嘅朋友變成敵人"},{"pid":"f3efab6301f6f04790b7e2fc7e6e1ff060793386","tid":1493424,"uid":53988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:58:36.000Z","msg":"大陸有外匯管制 大把廠商想匯錢返自已都有難度呀 仲講走資<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論:講多10年都冇可能支爆"},{"pid":"75f3b6cafedee4a1846b7eaa57cddd5a7d977f73","tid":1493424,"uid":298012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:58:50.000Z","msg":"我係侵侵就先叫維尼帶晒佢d左右手一齊去美國傾野，然後搵人火燒後欄迫佢支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358a680dd3e07b12398087d1dc03f759d3e538f3","tid":1493424,"uid":105353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:59:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4592ce492f9bad28d266417ad86184aa4bb05b1","tid":1493424,"uid":29510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f918cb116b25412eef70d7abb066fce3babaef57","tid":1493424,"uid":4811,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:54:48.000Z","msg":"由外而內再到返外⋯⋯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:00:02.000Z","msg":"岩呀<br />\n要造到一鼓不信任風氣<br />\n將香港前途同中國經濟綑綁"},{"pid":"a6d6caef1c459c64f1e980e81ccf9943807436a9","tid":1493424,"uid":38982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:00:04.000Z","msg":"成功令美國制裁中國官員"},{"pid":"2a2832f186870d98b2e196b4efb1c41a2adca0db","tid":1493424,"uid":274435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:00:58.000Z","msg":"其實條一帶一路就快收皮<br />\n支那啲債務一夠冇錢還就骨牌效應<br />\n<br />\n全世界經濟同佢割蓆佢就變成第二個北韓"},{"pid":"2535b38a40cdd795822d904f4a915753e21c667a","tid":1493424,"uid":4811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"51cd6c1b84bb14a6dde7885a9ba39959bbf95198","tid":1493424,"uid":92188,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:57:48.000Z","msg":"中國已經r爛塊面，之前仲想包裝自己做文明大國，輸出劣性文化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:03:34.000Z","msg":"儒家包裝嘅納粹極權"},{"pid":"1ad820e0628be502af6a78bc2498a493c1ffda2c","tid":1493424,"uid":29510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f3efab6301f6f04790b7e2fc7e6e1ff060793386","tid":1493424,"uid":53988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:58:36.000Z","msg":"大陸有外匯管制 大把廠商想匯錢返自已都有難度呀 仲講走資<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論:講多10年都冇可能支爆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:03:53.000Z","msg":"其實唔一定要實係爆<br />\n但係你見到中美貿易戰都搞到中國、香港經濟急轉直下<br />\n冇野冇可能<br />\n而家中共各方面經濟條件都有困難, 呢個係一個契機<br />\n<br />\n真正目的, 佢支唔支爆我理撚得佢, <br />\n係博佢唔想因為香港問題, 而賠上大陸經濟<br />\n應承5大訴求, 完左件事佢"},{"pid":"868308a5bf3e200319e598aef414be762e412784","tid":1493424,"uid":233843,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:09:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76f72d9497cc858381b41b500b2ae6d1d690fc4c","tid":1493424,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:27:33.000Z","msg":"支共比歷史上其他邪惡政權還要難對付"},{"pid":"bf7dfdfb6aeed0bf7f3d060ed243caa53f787163","tid":1493424,"uid":29510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"868308a5bf3e200319e598aef414be762e412784","tid":1493424,"uid":233843,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:09:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:45:42.000Z","msg":"有冇睇內文<br />\n侵侵當然都係睇利益, 有利自己咪做<br />\n而家我唔係真係要支爆<br />\n而係要綑綁中國經濟同香港前途<br />\n侵侵從來都係得把口講, 係冇用<br />\n<br />\n同時侵侵上年係呼籲全球一齊去抵制華為5G技術<br />\n歐洲都唔撚理<br />\n而家表面上, 我地係幫侵侵, 拉攏世界各地人士抵制中國野<br />\n實際係俾中共知道香港係麻煩o既源頭, 因為抵制中國貨係由香港人發起<br />\n博中共因為唔想賠上辛苦經營30年o既聲譽、中國經濟, 而答應香港麻煩友o既5大訴求"},{"pid":"3182f4de75354df54ff10093a66f5b99b8ecf362","tid":1493424,"uid":29510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:04:45.000Z","msg":"推到外國手足做野"},{"pid":"39bc375cbb721f2741b01c8c6cef329d75f4e1b5","tid":1493424,"uid":233843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:07:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8aecd23422b014635a029d25ba59e85c0410178f","tid":1493424,"uid":266752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:12:07.000Z","msg":"Chinazi Chinazi Chinazi"},{"pid":"3ae03d7d7ac8b7c1e9be3ab2529db63ce38ad906","tid":1493424,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:29:31.000Z","msg":"圍魏救趙<br />\nPush <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff5cfd24510a8468713a369fa7faf98343793b8","tid":1493424,"uid":167956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:36:30.000Z","msg":"首先香港人罷買中國貨先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再推廣到全世界<br />\n外國人有時唔起香港<br />\n支持唔到<br />\n但罷買中國貨呢度都可以出一分力<br />\n外國人應該可以幫手支持到<br />\n<br />\n再持續將中國妖魔化同恐怖化<br />\n例如中國留學生<br />\n明明係知識份子<br />\n但就做納粹手勢等<br />\n等無人敢去中國<br />\n<br />\n到時中國出口大受影響<br />\n帶動進一步大量失業<br />\n外國人都唔敢去中國同投資<br />\n形成嚴重貿易逆差<br />\n<br />\n呢兩方面值得文宣做推廣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f05cf9cb77feea9e745268adc137602a50dcbd","tid":1493424,"uid":21654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:38:19.000Z","msg":"首先要香港人戒左淘寶先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f1e436b011e14607e43970ed4715551ef7c655","tid":1493424,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3efab6301f6f04790b7e2fc7e6e1ff060793386","tid":1493424,"uid":53988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:58:36.000Z","msg":"大陸有外匯管制 大把廠商想匯錢返自已都有難度呀 仲講走資<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論:講多10年都冇可能支爆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:38:50.000Z","msg":"陸路運錢黨"}]}